snippet.title: Super Pocket Atari & Technos Edition!
snippet.description:
The critically acclaimed Super Pocket from HyperMegaTech! is BACK FOR 2024, in two great new Editions!

Super Pocket Atari Edition brings 50 Atari Classics in the palm of your hands from the Arcade, 2600, 5200, 7800 and Lynx. The Super Pocket Technos Edition brings 15 great games from the creators of Double Dragon Series including arcade greats, console and handheld classics like River City Ransom!
 
ONLY £49/$59/€59 EACH!
 
Pre-order from July 31st, available October 2024!

Also available - Super Pocket Atari Special Edition. Limited to 2600 units in a special woodgrain design! Available from Funstock. Pre-orders are open RIGHT NOW!


Visit the website to find your local retailer: 
https://www.hypermegatech.com
